{"type": "article", "id": 60974, "title": "优酷拿下央视春晚直播权，Instagram 破纪录蛋的秘密揭晓 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-02-03T05:01:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 4361, "name": "超级碗"}, {"id": 1502, "name": "春晚"}, {"id": 1700, "name": "优酷"}, {"id": 4652, "name": "Hulu"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 45, "image": "img/article/article_show/201902031218204terEDWnBi5PTpHO.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">超级碗广告 2019 </h3><p line=\"nOJx\"><b><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3KuQ4i_VSso\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Olay 首次呈现在超级碗上的广告 “Killer Skin”</a>，</b>营造了恐怖片的气氛，展现产品对皮肤状况的惊奇改变。片中女主角 Sarah Michelle Gellar 之前出演过经典恐怖电影《惊声尖叫2》、《我知道你去年夏天做了什么》。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=v08346tpdki\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"BqCw\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tDakI68u2xE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>亚马逊的 Prime Video 今年将再次出现在超级碗上，</b></a>广告片为接下来推出的原创系列节目 “Hanna” 预热。女主角的问题“我是谁？我该如何适应”能引起很多年轻女孩共鸣。跑酷场景则可以得到年轻的男性观众的关注。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=v08342tp815\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"fuzy\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tDakI68u2xE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>品客的超级碗广告 Sad Device 继续推销它的 “Stack” 多种口味吃法，</b></a>今年多了一个智能设备，它能够说出口味的排列组合数目，但是却永远没法体验和品尝。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=o08357vi7fm\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"8U0z\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B5FzKB5TW0Y\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>现代汽车的超级碗广告 “Elevator” 风格幽默，</b></a>通过不同楼层的特点展示 Shopper Assurance （购物者保障） 是处于上层的服务。这项服务在网上操作即可，消费者购买汽车更为便捷和透明。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=x08359sulgo\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"7c5H\"><b><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3hGv_yBmXz4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tony Romo 再次和 Skechers 合作出现在今年的超级碗广告中</a>，</b>他强调生活中喜欢“easy”的方式，比如扫地人和手机应用等便捷的选择，类比 Skechers 的无系带运动鞋同样如此。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=x0833xl2y56\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"lkWr\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/1781741732/4335200051800984\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>999 感冒灵推出四款高腰及胸的秋裤，</b></a>海报的整体设计风格可能是追随最近很流行的审丑风。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190203122042CL73Ffr9lxTEkque.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.697128\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190203122043DS9pKvtkfYgihw7r.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190203122042BQR7jICTEMkfq9tX.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190203122042BErXKWi9jyUwsAVO.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190203122043BX6hVNRYvHwt13Ma.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=d0834030o1u\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"ZyI8\">死侍 2 在发布了一组中国风的宣传海报大获好评之后，又接连发布了几组新春风格的，<b>加入<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4332636094465248?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">吊钱</a>、<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4333013582569725?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">门神</a>和<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4333361256317980?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">福字</a>这些传统春节习俗</b>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190203122120ERHpecvyOY9X5Lgq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190203122120evSBcNXEjYqG1yPk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190203122136b7m2lNJcGOzEUhCa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019020312212057eLioAaMrDZHyKN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190203122120MYQsq3dfhn2LPSey.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.459259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201902031221211G6u2tpbT7s9vEqm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201902031221216pL4B1VkRsb5j73c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"TX1H\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/world_record_egg/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>1 月份在 Instagram 上热门的“世界纪录蛋”昨天揭秘了真相，是美国流媒体 Hulu 的超级碗推广广告。</b></a>该账号之后陆续发布了几只破裂的蛋，但昨天系上了鞋带。并且配图文字说明：“等待结束了”，提醒大家 Hulu 是可以最早观看超级碗的平台。现在第一张蛋的点赞数已经超过 5200 万，有 990 多万粉丝关注这个账户。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201902031222397qbCGtYKHjSBoJvc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190203122239nqxXcym8gebQBM2r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>其他，也很重要</h3><p line=\"xdLq\"><b><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzNTI4NTU5OQ==&amp;mid=2247491974&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=308acb33825239d3fade70df5fc31e8b&amp;chksm=e8ebdcb6df9c55a0a882fb443f643e0491a431cd301a652f9ecdf577314ab275b8891a0759c5&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0202a1ha28AUSGYQbmHtx629&amp;key=1dd4e38074aa080da10f997f22c57425744ccf979e7f888751faddff2a2aa906b5b6e49c1cd93d4f5f2e7a639aa42ac3b8fcaf9c6dceea48290b66a8efb411de94881a0ed748da05642dd65b8f2a2ce7&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=j1N9O89E0O71mIjWTQN3PyrSAU3o6Z7jgpgXq3%2FFvHKAgwLu7IqcgxJJAMowUqZ5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">优酷</a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzNTI4NTU5OQ==&amp;mid=2247491974&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=308acb33825239d3fade70df5fc31e8b&amp;chksm=e8ebdcb6df9c55a0a882fb443f643e0491a431cd301a652f9ecdf577314ab275b8891a0759c5&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0202a1ha28AUSGYQbmHtx629&amp;key=1dd4e38074aa080da10f997f22c57425744ccf979e7f888751faddff2a2aa906b5b6e49c1cd93d4f5f2e7a639aa42ac3b8fcaf9c6dceea48290b66a8efb411de94881a0ed748da05642dd65b8f2a2ce7&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=j1N9O89E0O71mIjWTQN3PyrSAU3o6Z7jgpgXq3%2FFvHKAgwLu7IqcgxJJAMowUqZ5\" target=\"_blan